data.description: Escape the ordinary with this extraordinary 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom bungalow in the heart of East Point. Explore the endless possibilities this unique property offers while effortlessly blending modern sophistication with urban convenience. Upon entering, you're immediately enveloped in an abundance of natural light that gracefully complements the open, well-designed layout. This bungalow, distinguished by its timeless aesthetics, provides a versatile backdrop for your creative vision. For those with a keen eye on investment opportunities, this property offers a unique prospect as an Airbnb gem. Boasting five adaptable bedrooms, it's poised to provide an income stream while exuding an air of refined hospitality. The fully finished basement adds a whole new level of possibilities. One of the standout features of this basement is the kitchenette. Whether it's for entertaining guests, preparing meals, or supporting a separate living arrangement, this kitchen is a true bonus. The basement is complete with a separate entrance, making it ideal for in-laws, teenagers, or an Airbnb opportunity! Complete with 2 spacious bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a living area for relaxation, it provides privacy and independence while still being connected to the main house. Escape to your own secluded sanctuary with a beautifully landscaped backyard, perfect for outdoor relaxation and the lush gardens create a serene environment to entertain or unwind. Beyond the property, the location is the ultimate clincher. A mere stone's throw from Main Street, you're privy to a plethora of boutique shops, esteemed dining establishments, and an eclectic array of entertainment options. Here, every day unfolds as an exhilarating adventure. Nature enthusiasts will be drawn to the tranquility of Sykes Park, providing an idyllic escape for outdoor recreation. Commuters will find the proximity of the East Point MARTA station a valuable asset, facilitating a seamless connection to the heart of Atlanta. Situated close to the Atlanta Airport, Tyler Perry Studios, and easy access to major highways. This bungalow offers not only a residence but a refined way of life. Whether seeking your own private sanctuary, a promising investment opportunity, or a harmonious blend of both, this property adapts to your unique aspirations, enabling you to enjoy life on your terms. Elevate your lifestyle and seize the opportunity to make this distinguished bungalow your own and experience the epitome of refined living in East Point.
